arStrings.szText:
Casting a {c_important}Cutthroat{/c} Skill grants a stack of {c_important}Momentum{/c}. Casting a Non-{c_important}Cutthroat{/c} Skill removes a stack of {c_important}Momentum{/c}. 

For each stack of {c_important}Momentum{/c}, you gain:
{icon:bullet,1.2} {c_number}[SF_3} * 100|%|]{/c} Damage Reduction
{icon:bullet,1.2} {c_number}[SF_3} * 100|%|]{/c} Maximum Energy
{icon:bullet,1.2} {c_number}[SF_3} * 100|%x|]{/c} Energy Regeneration
{icon:bullet,1.2} {c_number}[SF_3} * 100|%+|]{/c} Movement Speed
{icon:bullet,1.2} {c_number}[SF_8} * 100|%x|]{/c} Increased Damage

Maximum of {c_number}[{SF_1}||]{/c} Stacks.
